task id=1 status=todo {
    title "Initialize project from scaffold"
    description "Takes a project name and a git remote URL as input.\n\n1. Update README.md: replace scaffold-specific content (clone instructions, title) with the new project name\n2. Update CLAUDE.md: update project overview to reflect the new project\n3. Update `client/index.html` `<title>` with the new project name\n4. Update root `package.json` `\"name\"` with the new project name (lowercase/hyphenated)\n5. `rm -rf .git && git init`\n6. `git add -A && git commit -m \"Initial commit\"`\n7. `git remote add origin <url> && git push -u origin main`"
